  "[[5, 0],[0, 3]]": "[5,0],[0,3]]",
  "[[3, 0],[0, 5]]": "[[3,0],[0,5]]",
  "Non-uniform scaling uses a diagonal matrix with different scale factors: [[3,0],[0,5]] maps (x,y) to (3x, 5y). The x-axis is stretched by 3 and the y-axis by 5.": "非统一缩放使用具有不同比例因子的对角矩阵:[[3,0,[0,5] 地图(x,y)至(3x,5y)。x轴拉伸3,Y轴为5。",
  "What is a horizontal shear matrix in R^2 with shear factor k?": "R2 中带有剪切因子 k 的水平剪切矩阵是什么 ?",
  "[[1, 0],[0, k]]": "[[1,0],[0,k]]]",
