  "det([[1,k],[0,1]]) = 1*1 - k*0 = 1. Shear transformations always have determinant 1, meaning they preserve area even though they distort shapes.": "det([[1,k],[0,1]) = 1*1 - k*0 = 1. 剪切变形总是有决定性因素1, 意即保留面积, 即使它们扭曲形状 。",
  "What is the inverse of the scaling matrix [[3, 0],[0, 2]]?": "缩放矩阵[[[3]、[0]、[0]、[2]]的反差是什么?",
