  "The inverse of a diagonal matrix [[a,0],[0,b]] is [[1/a, 0],[0, 1/b]], provided a and b are nonzero. So the inverse is [[1/3, 0],[0, 1/2]], which undoes the scaling.": "对角矩阵[[[a,0,0,b]]的反面是[[1/a,0,[0,1b]]],条件是a和b为非零。因此反面是[[1/3,0],[0,1/2]],它推翻了缩放。",
  "What happens to a unit square under the shear [[1, 2],[0, 1]]?": "剪切[[1,2],[0,1]]下的一个单位方形发生什么情况?",
  "It becomes a rectangle": "它变成了一个矩形",
  "It becomes a larger square": "变成一个更大的广场",
  "It becomes a triangle": "变成三角形",
  "It becomes a parallelogram with the same area": "成为同一区域的平行图",
  "A shear transforms a square into a parallelogram. The base stays fixed (along x-axis) while the top edge slides horizontally. Since det = 1, the area is preserved even though the shape changes.": "剪切将正方形转换成平行图。 基底保持固定( lax- 轴) , 而顶端边缘水平滑动。 自 det = 1 开始, 即使形状改变, 区域也会被保留 。",
  "If you scale by factor 2 and then scale by factor 3, what single scaling factor achieves the same result?": "如果按因数2乘以乘以2,然后按因数3乘以乘以3,哪个单一因数得出相同结果?",
  "6": "6, 6, 6, 6, 6, 6, 6, 6, 6, 6, 6, 6, 6, 6",
