  "5": "5 5",
  "Composing uniform scalings multiplies the factors: (3I)(2I) = 6I. So scaling by 2 then by 3 is the same as scaling by 6. This is because scalar matrices commute and multiply component-wise.": "将统一缩放组合成成乘以因子 : (3I)(2I) = 6I。 因此, 缩放乘以 2 乘以 3 与 缩放乘以 6 相同, 这是因为 运算矩阵通勤和乘以组件 。",
  "What is 'scaling' as a linear transformation?": "什么是线性变换的“ 缩放” ?",
  "A transformation that projects onto a subspace": "投入子空间的转换",
  "A transformation that rotates vectors by a fixed angle": "以固定角度旋转矢量的转换",
  "A transformation that adds a constant to each coordinate": "在每个坐标上加一个常数的变换",
  "A transformation that multiplies each coordinate by a (possibly different) constant factor": "使每个坐标乘以一个(可能不同)常数因数的变换",
  "Scaling is a linear transformation represented by a diagonal matrix that multiplies each coordinate by a constant factor. Uniform scaling uses the same factor for all axes; non-uniform scaling uses different factors per axis.": "缩放是一个线性变换,其代表的是一个对角矩阵,该矩阵将每个坐标乘以一个不变系数。统一缩放对所有轴都使用相同的系数;非统一缩放使用不同的轴因子。",
  "What is a 'shear' transformation?": "什么是“听力”转变?",
  "A transformation that rotates and scales simultaneously": "同时旋转和尺度的转换",
  "A transformation that cuts vectors in half": "将矢量减半的转变",
  "A transformation that maps all vectors to a single line": "将所有矢量映射成单线的转换",
  "A transformation that displaces points proportionally to their distance from a fixed line, while keeping the fixed direction unchanged": "使定点与其与固定线的距离成正比取出点数的转换,同时保持固定方向不变",
  "A shear displaces each point in a fixed direction by an amount proportional to its signed distance from a line parallel to that direction. One axis stays fixed while the other tilts, like pushing the top of a deck of cards sideways.": "剪切将每个点在固定方向上换成一个与该方向平行的线段的签名距离成比例的值。 一个轴保持固定,而另一个斜面则保持固定,比如将纸牌侧面的甲板推到顶端。",
  "What does 'dilation' mean in linear algebra?": "线性代数中的“衰变”是什么意思?",
  "A rotation by a small angle": "由小角度旋转",
  "A reflection followed by a scaling": "反省,然后是缩放",
  "A uniform scaling with factor greater than 1 that enlarges all distances from the origin": "统一缩放,因数大于1,扩大与原产地的所有距离",
  "Any transformation that changes shape": "改变形状的任何转换",
  "A dilation is a uniform scaling by a factor k > 1, which enlarges all vectors uniformly from the origin. Every distance is multiplied by k, so shapes grow but maintain their proportions.": "膨胀是乘以因子 k > 1 的统一缩放, 使所有矢量均从源次扩大。 每个距离乘以 k, 所以形状会生长, 但仍保持比例 。",
  "What does 'contraction' mean in linear algebra?": "线性代数中的“合同”是什么意思?",
  "A shear with a negative parameter": "带有负参数的剪切",
  "A uniform scaling with factor between 0 and 1 that shrinks all distances toward the origin": "统一缩放,因数在0到1之间,向原产地的距离缩小",
  "A transformation that reduces the number of dimensions": "A. 能够减少尺寸数目的转变",
  "The inverse of any transformation": "任何转变的逆向",
  "A contraction is a uniform scaling by 0 < k < 1, shrinking all vectors toward the origin. It is the opposite of a dilation -- distances decrease uniformly while shapes maintain their proportions.": "缩缩是平均缩放0 < k < 1, 将所有矢量压缩到源头。 缩缩与推算相反 -- -- 距离一致降低,而形状则保持比例。",
  "What does 'non-uniform scaling' (anisotropic scaling) mean?": "“非统一缩放”(异体缩放)意味着什么?",
  "Scaling by different factors along different axes": "不同轴上不同因素的缩放",
  "Scaling that varies over time": "随时间变化的缩放",
  "Scaling that applies only to some vectors": "仅适用于某些矢量的缩放",
  "Scaling by the same factor along all axes": "在所有轴上以相同的系数缩放",
  "Non-uniform (anisotropic) scaling applies different scale factors along different axes, represented by a diagonal matrix with unequal entries. A circle becomes an ellipse under non-uniform scaling.": "非统一( anisotopic) 缩放在不同的轴上应用不同的缩放因子, 不同的轴由带有不平等条目的对角矩阵代表。 一个圆会变成非统一缩放下的椭圆 。",
  "What is a 'shear factor'?": "什么是“听觉因素”?",
  "The constant k that determines how much displacement occurs per unit distance from the fixed line": "确定距离固定线每单位距离多少位移位的恒定 k k",
  "The determinant of the shear matrix": "剪剪矩阵的决定因素",
  "The angle of rotation in the shear": "剪切中的旋转角度",
  "The number of shear operations applied": "适用的剪切作业数量",
  "The shear factor k is the proportionality constant: for each unit of y-coordinate, the x-coordinate shifts by k units (in a horizontal shear). Larger |k| means more distortion.": "剪切系数 k 是相称性常数 : 对于 Y 坐标的每个单位, 由 k 单位( 在水平剪切中) x 坐标移动 。 大    意指更大的扭曲 。",
  "What is an 'affine transformation'?": "什么是“牛油果变异”?",
  "A transformation that preserves all angles": "保存所有角度的转换",
  "Any transformation that can be represented by a matrix": "可以用矩阵表代表的任何转换",
  "A transformation that only involves scaling": "仅涉及规模的转型",
  "A linear transformation followed by a translation: T(x) = Ax + b": "直线转换,然后翻译: T(x) = Ax + b",
  "An affine transformation is of the form T(x) = Ax + b, combining a linear transformation (matrix A) with a translation (vector b). Unlike pure linear transformations, affine transformations can shift the origin.": "线形变换为表T(x) = Ax + b,将线性变换(矩阵A)与译文(矢量b)合并。 与纯线性变换不同的是,线性变换可以改变原产物。",
  "What does 'area scaling factor' mean for a 2D linear transformation?": "2D 线性转换的“面积缩放系数”意味着什么?",
  "The largest entry in the matrix in accordance with classical theory": "根据古典理论在矩阵中的最大条目",
  "The sum of the diagonal entries squared when applying fundamental principles": "在适用基本原则时方形对角条目总和",
  "The trace of the matrix, particularly regarding region under the given assumptions": "矩阵的跟踪,特别是根据特定假设对区域进行的跟踪",
  "The absolute value of the determinant, |det(A)|, which gives the factor by which areas are multiplied": "确定值的绝对值 det(A) ,它给出了区域乘以的系数",
  "The area scaling factor is |det(A)|. Any region with area S is transformed to a region with area |det(A)| * S. For a scaling matrix [[a,0],[0,b]], the area factor is |ab|.": "面积缩放系数为det(A)。有区域S的任何区域都转换成区域{det(A)*S。对于缩放矩阵[[a,0,0,b]],面积系数为ab}。",
  "What is a 'stretch' in one direction?": "一个方向的“伸展”是什么?",
  "A shear applied twice, particularly regarding leaving within the typical range of values": "剪切两次适用两次,特别是在离开典型值范围内的情况下。",
  "A rotation that elongates vectors within the typical range of values": "使矢量在典型值范围内变长的旋转",
  "A non-uniform scaling that changes the scale factor along exactly one axis while keeping others at 1": "非统一缩放,使一个轴轴上的比额表因数完全改变,而其他轴数则维持在1",
  "A projection onto a single axis when evaluated systematically": "系统评价时投射到单一轴",
  "A stretch in one direction scales one axis by factor k while leaving others unchanged. For example, [[k,0],[0,1]] stretches along x by k while y is unchanged. Circles become ellipses with this transformation.": "一个方向的伸展以系数 k 衡量一个轴,而其他轴则保持不变。例如,[[k,0],[0,1]] 沿xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxy y 不变。圆形随着这种变换而变成省略号。",
  "What does 'squeeze mapping' refer to?": "“ 冷冻映射” 指的是什么 ?",
  "A shear that compresses vectors": "压缩矢量的剪剪",
  "A transformation that makes all vectors unit length": "使所有矢量单位长度的转换",
  "A scaling that stretches one axis while compressing the other so that areas are preserved (det = 1)": "伸展一个轴的缩放,同时压缩另一个轴,以便区域被保护(检测=1)",
  "A projection onto a lower-dimensional space": "投射到低维空间",
  "A squeeze mapping like [[k,0],[0,1/k]] stretches one axis by k and compresses the other by 1/k. Since det = k * (1/k) = 1, area is preserved. It is used in hyperbolic geometry and Lorentz transformations.": "类似 [[k,0,0,0,1] 的挤压绘图将一个轴用 k 伸展,并将另一个轴压缩为 1/k。 由于 dot = k * (1/k) = 1, 区域被保存, 它被用于双曲几何和 Lorentz 转换 。",
  "A graphic designer needs to make a logo 150% wider and 80% taller. If the logo's center point is at (4, 5), where does the center move to after this non-uniform scaling?": "图形设计师需要将标识宽150%,高80%。 如果标识的中点是( 4, 5) , 中心在非统一缩放后移动到哪里 ?",
  "(5.2, 5.8)": "(5.2、5.8)",
  "(4, 4)": "(4,4)",
  "(6, 5)": "(6,5)",
  "The scaling matrix is [[1.5, 0],[0, 0.8]]. Applied to (4,5): (1.5*4, 0.8*5) = (6, 4). The logo's center moves right (wider) and down (shorter), reflecting the non-uniform stretch.": "缩放矩阵[[1.5,0],[0,0.8]]。应用到(4,5): (1.5*4,0.8*5) = (6,4) 。标志的中心向右(宽)向下(短)移动,反映非统一范围。",
  "An architect uses a shear transformation to design a slanted building facade. The base of the building spans from (0,0) to (10,0), and the height is 20 units. If a horizontal shear with k = 0.3 is applied, where does the top-left corner (0, 20) move?": "建筑师用剪切变形来设计倾斜的建筑外墙。 建筑的底部从0,0到10,0, 高度为20个单位。 如果使用K=0. 3的横向剪切, 左上角( 0, 20) 移动在哪里 ?",
  "(0.3, 20)": "(0.3,20)",
  "(0, 26)": "(0,26)",
  "(20, 6)": "(20,6)",
  "(6, 20)": "(6,20)",
  "[[1, 0.3],[0, 1]] * (0, 20) = (0 + 0.3*20, 0 + 1*20) = (6, 20). The top of the building shifts 6 units to the right while maintaining the same height, creating the slanted facade effect.": "[1,0.3],[0,1]]],*(0,20)=(0+0.3*20,0+1*20)=(6,20) 建筑物的顶部将6个单元向右移动,同时保持同样的高度,造成倾斜的外形效应。",
  "A printer needs to correct for paper stretching during printing. The paper stretches 5% in the horizontal direction and 2% in the vertical direction. What pre-compensation scaling matrix should be applied to the digital image so it prints correctly?": "打印机在打印过程中需要校正纸张伸展。 纸张在水平方向为5%,在垂直方向为2%。 对数字图像应应用什么前补偿缩放矩阵,以便正确打印?",
  "[[0.05, 0],[0, 0.02]]": "[0.05, 0, [0, 0.02]",
  "[[1/1.05, 0],[0, 1/1.02]]": "[1/1.05,0,[0,1/1.02]]",
  "[[1.05, 0],[0, 1.02]]": "[105,0,[0,1.02]]",
  "[[0.95, 0],[0, 0.98]]": "[0.95,0],[0,0.98]",
  "The paper stretch applies [[1.05, 0],[0, 1.02]] to the image. To compensate, pre-multiply by the inverse: [[1/1.05, 0],[0, 1/1.02]]. After stretching, the final result is [[1.05, 0],[0, 1.02]] * [[1/1.05, 0],[0, 1/1.02]] = I, restoring the correct proportions.": "纸面伸展适用于图像[[[1.05,0],[0,1.02]]。为了补偿,先乘以倒数:[1/1.05,0],[0,1/1.02]]。在伸展后,最后结果为[[1.05,0,1.02] *[1/1.05,0],[0,1/1.02]] =I,恢复正确比例。",
  "A video editor applies a horizontal shear with k=1 to create an italic text effect. The letter 'I' is represented by corners (0,0), (1,0), (1,5), (0,5). What shape does the letter become?": "视频编辑器使用 K=1 的水平剪切来创建斜体文字效果。 字母“ I” 由角表示 (0, 0, 1, 0, 1, 5, (0, 5) 。 该字母会变成什么形状 ?",
  "A parallelogram with corners (0,0), (1,0), (2,5), (1,5)": "角平行图(0,0),(1,0),(2,5),(1,5)",
