  "A cartographer needs to project a map region. The east-west scale is 1 cm = 10 km and the north-south scale is 1 cm = 5 km. What scaling matrix converts real-world kilometers to map centimeters?": "制图师需要预测地图区域。 东西级比例为1厘米=10公里, 南北级比例为1厘米=5公里。 什么缩放矩阵转换实际世界公里来绘制厘米?",
  "[[0.2, 0],[0, 0.1]]": "[0.2,0],[0,0.1]]",
  "[[0.1, 0],[0, 0.1]]": "[0.1,0],[0,0],[0,0]]]",
  "[[10, 0],[0, 5]]": "[[10,0],[0,5]]",
  "[[0.1, 0],[0, 0.2]]": "[0.1,0,[0,0,0.2]]",
  "1 cm = 10 km means 1 km = 0.1 cm (east-west), and 1 cm = 5 km means 1 km = 0.2 cm (north-south). The matrix [[0.1, 0],[0, 0.2]] converts km to cm, giving the correct map scale.": "1厘米=10公里=1公里=0.1厘米(东-西),1厘米=5公里=1公里=0.2厘米(北-南)。",
  "A mechanical engineer models wind load on a building. Wind at 45 degrees applies a shear force. The deformation is modeled by composing a horizontal shear (k=0.5) with a vertical shear (k=0.5). What is the combined transformation matrix?": "机械工程师模型对建筑物进行风负负。45度的风运用剪切力。变形模型是用垂直剪切(k=0.5)的横向剪切(k=0.5)制成的。组合变形矩阵是什么?",
  "[[1, 1],[1, 1]]": "[[1,1]、[1,1]]",
  "[[1, 0.5],[0.5, 1]]": "[1,0.5],[0.5,1]]",
  "[[1.25, 0.5],[0.5, 1]]": "[1.25、0.5]、[0.5、1]]",
  "[[2, 0.5],[0.5, 2]]": "[2,0.5],[0.5,2]]",
  "Horizontal shear: H = [[1, 0.5],[0, 1]]. Vertical shear: V = [[1, 0],[0.5, 1]]. Composing H after V: HV = [[1*1+0.5*0.5, 1*0+0.5*1],[0*1+1*0.5, 0*0+1*1]] = [[1.25, 0.5],[0.5, 1]].": "水平剪切:H = [[1,0.5],[0,1]]]。垂直剪切:V = [[1,0],[0.5,1]]。在V之后加成H :HV = [[[1,1+0.5*0.5,1,*0+0.5*1],[0*1+1*0.5,0*0+1*1]]] =[1.25,0.5],[0.5,1]]。",
  "A biologist magnifies a cell image by 400x horizontally and 400x vertically. The original cell measures 10 micrometers by 5 micrometers. What are the dimensions of the magnified image in micrometers?": "生物学家将细胞图象放大400x水平和400x垂直。 最初的细胞用10微米乘5微米。 放大图象在微米中的尺寸是多少?",
  "4000 by 5": "5比4000 5比4000",
  "40 by 20": "40x20 40x20",
  "410 by 405": "410 乘 405 乘 405 乘 410 乘 405",
  "4000 by 2000": "到2000年时4000 000",
  "The uniform scaling matrix [[400, 0],[0, 400]] maps (10, 5) to (400*10, 400*5) = (4000, 2000). Uniform scaling preserves the aspect ratio: the image is 400 times larger in both dimensions.": "统一缩放矩阵[[400]、[0]、[400]]地图(10、5)至(400*10、400*5)=(400,2000)=(400,2000)统一缩放比例保持了方位比:两个维度的图像都大400倍。",
  "A typography designer creates an oblique font by applying a shear transformation [[1, 0.4],[0, 1]] to upright letters. If the top of the letter 'T' is at (0, 12), where does it move?": "打字设计师通过对直立字母应用剪切转换[[[1,0.4],[0,1]]]来创建斜字体。如果字母“T”的顶部为 0, 12, 它移动到哪里 ?",
  "(4.8, 12)": "(4.8、12)",
  "(0, 16.8)": "(0,16.8)",
  "(12, 4.8)": "(12,4.8)",
  "(0.4, 12)": "(0.4、12)",
  "[[1, 0.4],[0, 1]] * (0, 12) = (0 + 0.4*12, 0 + 1*12) = (4.8, 12). The top of the T shifts 4.8 units to the right while staying at height 12, creating the slanted oblique style.": "[1,0.4],[0,1]]] *(0,12)=(0+0.4*12,0+1*12)=(4.8,12) =(4.8,12) T的顶部将4.8个单位向右移动,在高度12处停留,形成斜斜斜的斜体样式。",
  "A film studio needs to convert widescreen footage (16:9) to standard format (4:3). They scale the horizontal dimension by 3/4 and the vertical by 1 (no change). A character at position (160, 90) in the original: where are they in the converted frame?": "电影制片厂需要将宽屏片段(16:9)转换为标准格式(4:3),将水平维度缩放3/4,将垂直维度缩放1(不变)。 原版位置( 160, 90) 的字符: 在转换框中, 字符的位置( 160, 90) 在哪里 ?",
  "(120, 90)": "(120、90)",
  "(120, 67.5)": "(120,67.5)",
  "(213.3, 90)": "(213.3,90)",
  "(160, 67.5)": "(160,67.5)",
  "[[3/4, 0],[0, 1]] * (160, 90) = (0.75*160, 1*90) = (120, 90). The horizontal dimension is compressed to 75% while vertical stays the same, which matches the width ratio change from 16:9 to 4:3.": "[[3/4,0],[0,1]]]*(160,90)=(0.75*160,1*90)=(120,90)=(120,90) 水平维度压缩到75%,而垂直保持不变,与宽度比从16:9改为4:3相符。",
  "A geologist models tectonic plate deformation as a combination of compression along one axis and extension along the perpendicular axis, with no area change. If the compression factor is 0.8 along x, what must the extension factor be along y?": "地质学家模型构造板块变形,作为沿一个轴的压缩和沿直角轴的扩展的组合,没有区域变化。如果压缩系数是0.8和x,那么扩展系数必须跟随什么 y ?",
  "1.25": "1.25 1.25",
  "1.8": "1.8. 8",
  "0.8": "0.8. 0.8",
  "1.2": "1.2 1.2",
  "For area preservation, det([[0.8, 0],[0, k]]) = 0.8k = 1, so k = 1/0.8 = 1.25. The y-axis must extend by factor 1.25 to compensate for the 0.8 compression along x, maintaining constant area.": "对于区域保全,执行([[0.8,0],[0, k]])=0.8k = 1, so k = 1/0.8 = 1.25。 Y 轴必须扩大乘以1.25,以补偿x的0.8压缩,保持不变区域。"
